metadata.title: Golf Knickers Knee High Solid Color Cotton Socks for Men Women and Youth
features: RECOMMENDED SIZE CHART: Size 10-13 for Men. Size 6-9 for Ladies. Size 3-5 for Youth.
ULTRA COMFORT: With a blend of soft Combed Cotton, these solid socks will provide a comfortable fit for all-day use.
GREAT DESIGN: Our socks are made with a Super-Fine Seamless Toe, Built-In Heel, and Reinforced Toe. Seamless design allows for a good fit for each step taken.
MATCHES OUR GOLFKNICKERS: Each solid sock matches perfectly with our Golf Knickers. Make a statement on the course with the return to traditional golf apparel!
GREAT FOR ANY EVENT: All of our color are perfect for all different occasions. From Weddings, Dress, Groomsman, Golfers, Casual Wearers, or anything in between, find a color that works for you!
description: GolfKnickers.com presents our Over-the-Calf Solid Socks Collection; featuring 21 vibrant colors for our knee-high length socks. Each pair of Over-the-Calf Solid Socks serves as a fitting complement to our wide assortment of Golf Knicker outfits and accessories. Every Sock is designed using a comfortable Super-Fine Cotton Blend for maximum all-day comfort. Check out our matching Sweater Vests for the complete traditional look, along with any of our boldly-inspired Golf Knickers.
